replies.body:
Thank you so much for reading. I understand completely and hope my suggestion at least makes everyone a bit more considerate when dealing with deadlines and the ease of finding details of said deadlines. I know I might sound a bit whiny or spoiled so I apologize for that. Something as small as this doesn't diminish the love for this game at all. I will always support this game and Riot. Even if the icon never comes back, just knowing a few employees have read my plea and understood how I feel...it's really humbling.

Keep being awesome.

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
